{"tid":693180,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"2.5吋防水智能手機五臟俱全","createTime":"2018-06-07T09:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T00:48:49.000Z","uid":32706,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"03623336488e9a06f17dbf9811dc99e265d387bc","tid":693180,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:16:40.000Z","msg":"[im<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/171552_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F171552_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=85efe109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時，新款手機越嚟越細部，但去到智能手機年代，大家都想要一個大芒打機、上網或處理公務。Unihertz Atom卻反其道而行，推出小巧耐用嘅4G智能手機，結果喺KickStarter上集資亦同樣得到大班人支持，籌到超過目標資金10倍。<br />\n手機只有2.45吋240 x 432顯示屏，內置指紋辨識器與雙nano SIM插槽，八核CPU、4GB RAM及64GB ROM，運行Android 8.1 Oreo，前後鏡頭分別為8MP及16MP，側面配備自訂app啟動鍵。符合IP68防塵防水，Unihertz稱手機可於水中拍攝。預計10月付運，單售US$219（HK$1,718）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=26685&amp;catid=36&amp;utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fzen.yandex.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Fmobile%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D26685%26catid%3D36%26utm_referrer%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fzen.yandex.com&d=7IROXZj%2B%2BNRNlnucVjSBmdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=7587be15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=26685&amp;catid=36&amp;utm_referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fzen.yandex.com</a>"},{"pid":"be8886576aa892e6838b948b81bc5511c5890894","tid":693180,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:19:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/jellyphone/atom-world-s-smallest-4g-rugged-smartphone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fjellyphone%2Fatom-world-s-smallest-4g-rugged-smartphone&d=7IROXZj%2B%2BNRNlnucVjSBmdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f4ff361b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kicks